== Short Bio
I am currently on M.Eng program in artificial intelligence at [http://sigma.whu.edu.cn/ Sensing IntelliGence and MAchine learning(SIGMA) Lab] in the [https://cs.whu.edu.cn/ School of Computer Science], [https://www.whu.edu.cn/ Wuhan University], advised by Dr.[http://multimedia.whu.edu.cn/index.php?a=show&catid=69&id=141 Zengmao Wang] and Prof.[https://cs.whu.edu.cn/info/1019/2892.htm Bo Du] Before this I completed my B.Eng in Wuhan University of Computer Science and Technology. I am seeking 24fall Ph.D opportunity now. 

My research interests include machine learning(e.g., self-supervised & semi-supervised learning & active learning, reliable machine learning like learning and inference with Out-of-distribution data) and computer vision(e.g., classification and object detection).

